---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About — xCrypto24" description="xCrypto24 is a free real-time memecoin and cryptocurrency tracker with safety scores, trend detection, and new coin scanning." keywords="about xcrypto24, free crypto tracker, memecoin tracker, solana token scanner, real-time crypto">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebPage","name":"About — xCrypto24","url":"https://xcrypto24.com/about","description":"xCrypto24 is a free real-time memecoin and cryptocurrency tracker with safety scores, trend detection, and new coin scanning."})} />
  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:2rem auto;padding:0 1rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#fafafa;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">About xCrypto24</h1>
    <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">Free real-time crypto intelligence</p>

    <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:2rem;">xCrypto24 is a free memecoin and cryptocurrency tracking platform built for traders who want real-time data without the noise. No signup, no API keys, no premium tiers — just fast, reliable token intelligence.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">What We Do</h2>
    <div style="margin:1.5rem 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;">
      <div style="padding:1rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);background:rgba(88,28,135,0.15);">
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;"><span style="color:#a78bfa;font-weight:600;">Real-time Prices:</span> Live data from DexScreener across multiple chains</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);background:rgba(88,28,135,0.15);">
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;"><span style="color:#a78bfa;font-weight:600;">Safety Analysis:</span> RugCheck integration for holder distribution and risk scoring</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);background:rgba(88,28,135,0.15);">
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;"><span style="color:#a78bfa;font-weight:600;">Trend Detection:</span> Automatic status updates — Pumping, Consolidating, Dumping</p>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:1rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);background:rgba(88,28,135,0.15);">
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;"><span style="color:#a78bfa;font-weight:600;">New Coin Scanner:</span> Discover freshly listed tokens with one click</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">Our Promise</h2>
    <div style="margin:1.5rem 0;padding:1.2rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3);background:rgba(20,83,45,0.1);">
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#e4e4e7;line-height:1.7;"><strong style="color:#4ade80;">Free forever.</strong> No premium plans. No paywalls. No signup required. We believe crypto tools should be accessible to everyone — from first-time buyers to experienced degens.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">Built With</h2>
    <div style="margin:1.5rem 0;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.5rem;">
      <span style="padding:0.3rem 0.8rem;border-radius:6px;background:#16161f;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;font-size:0.8rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Astro</span>
      <span style="padding:0.3rem 0.8rem;border-radius:6px;background:#16161f;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;font-size:0.8rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Cloudflare Workers</span>
      <span style="padding:0.3rem 0.8rem;border-radius:6px;background:#16161f;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;font-size:0.8rem;color:#d4d4d8;">D1 Database</span>
      <span style="padding:0.3rem 0.8rem;border-radius:6px;background:#16161f;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;font-size:0.8rem;color:#d4d4d8;">DexScreener API</span>
      <span style="padding:0.3rem 0.8rem;border-radius:6px;background:#16161f;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;font-size:0.8rem;color:#d4d4d8;">RugCheck API</span>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:2.5rem;padding:1.2rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(139,92,246,0.1),rgba(109,40,217,0.05));border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;">
      <p style="color:#c084fc;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:500;">🪙 Start tracking coins now</p>
      <a href="/coins" style="padding:0.5rem 1.2rem;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#a78bfa,#7c3aed);color:white;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600;">Open Tracker →</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:2rem;text-align:center;">
      <a href="/" style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.85rem;text-decoration:none;">← Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
